*Bliže* kući, vozilo se ubrzalo. (The vehicle accelerated closer to the house.)

Putnik se iznenada osvrnuo *bliže* oko sebe. (The passenger suddenly looked around closer.)

*Bliže* večeri, vreme je postajalo sve hladnije. (As the evening drew closer, the weather was getting colder and colder.)

*Bliže* proleću, sve više cveća se pojavilo. (As spring drew closer, more and more flowers appeared.)

Kupac i prodavac su se dogovorili da se sastanu *bliže* sledećem mesecu. (The buyer and the seller agreed to meet closer to the next month.)